    {
      "name": "Poison Matrix (RAW reference)",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>Reference only — not used by the live save pipeline.</strong> This system replaces the poison matrix with a d20 + CN save; see Chapter 11 \"Poison Homebrew\" in the Rulebook Reference pack for the active rules. The RAW matrix below is preserved for lookup and for any GM who wants to run the original save-or-die resolution.</p><p>Constitution runs down the left side; Poison Strength runs across the top.</p><p>\"*\" means no effect.</p><p>A number means that many d6 of poison damage.</p><p>\"D\" means death unless the correct antidote is administered within two melee rounds.</p><p><em>Under the live homebrew: roll 1d20 + CN modifier vs. poison difficulty. Success = half damage, failure = full damage, never death on one cell.</em></p>\n    <div style=\"overflow-x:auto;margin:0.75rem 0\">\n      <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:max-content;min-width:100%;font-size:0.86rem\">\n        \n        <thead><tr><th>Constitution</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th><th>11</th><th>12</th><th>13</th><th>14</th><th>15</th><th>16</th><th>17</th><th>18</th></tr></thead>\n        <tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">18</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">17</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">16</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">15</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">14</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">13</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">12</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">11</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">10</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">9</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">8</th><td>*</td><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">7</th><td>*</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">6</th><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">5</th><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">4</th><td>3</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td>D</td><td